text:
Prototype purpose


This is a GitHub Pages-compatible static prototype. It demonstrates how the Excel-based tool can become a browser-based workflow with structured questions, transparent scoring, local save/export, and a workshop-ready summary report.


&lt;button class="tbca-btn" onclick="saveLocal()"&gt;Save in browser&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;button class="tbca-btn secondary" onclick="downloadJSON()"&gt;Export JSON&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;button class="tbca-btn light" onclick="window.print()"&gt;Print / Save PDF&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;button class="tbca-btn light" onclick="clearFormData()"&gt;Clear&lt;/button&gt;


For a first release on GitHub Pages, responses are stored in the participant’s browser and can be exported for workshop collation.




